<i>Aduh! Sial!</i>

07:25.771 --> 07:26.600
<i>Serang!</i>

07:32.169 --> 07:33.904
<i>Di mana dia,</i>
<i>astaga?</i>

07:34.195 --> 07:35.530
Pergi dari sini.
